data.description: Great home in an awesome location that is convenient to Raleigh, Wake Forest, Knigtdale and Rolesville. The home is located near I540, 64/264, I40 and easy commute downtown. NEWLY painted bedrooms 2 and 3, NEW carpet bedroom 2, NEW flooring both bathrooms and trim painted.  The home is secluded and is surrounded by beautiful trees. The backyard is fenced and has a great shed for storage. Enjoy the privacy from the back deck and the large backyard. A great place to call home.
